            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "\"As a parent, my experience at DPS Sushant Lok has been a constant source of positivity, where I witness my daughter's growth and witness the transformative power of education firsthand. \"DPSSL provides the best holistic education that goes beyond academics. They nurture not only my daughter's intellect but also her creativity, character, and social skills. It's a place where my daughter's overall development is given the utmost importance.",
          "publisher": {
