          },
          "datePublished": "2023-05-15",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We, as proud parents of Neehar (XII-D) and Anahad (VIII-A), would like to express our utmost satisfaction with the holistic development of our children during their time at Delhi Public School, Sushant Lok.\nWe would like to extend our heartfelt gratitude to the entire staff and management of the school for fostering an environment that has been instrumental in our children's growth. The faculty members at Delhi Public School, Sushant Lok are truly exceptional. Their profound knowledge, unwavering dedication, and genuine concern for the success of their students have left an indelible impression on us.\nWithout hesitation, we wholeheartedly recommend Delhi Public School, Sushant Lok to any parent who is in search of a quality education for their child. The school's unwavering commitment to academic excellence, coupled with the outstanding faculty, creates an exceptional learning and nurturing haven for every child to thrive and flourish.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
