            "name": "Anjali Sharma"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-23",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I recently visited DPS Sushant Lok and I am thoroughly impressed with the school. The school is positioned for progressive parents and I like to send my child to Delhi Public School, Sushant Lok , a learning institution with an open learning environment. The staff is friendly and welcoming and the classrooms are well-maintained, equipped with modern technology which makes teaching- learning interactive for the students. The curriculum is comprehensive and well-structured with balanced extracurricular activities for the overall development of the students. I highly recommend DPS Sushant Lok.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
